From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: automated <automated@example.com>
Date: Tue, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove sdbusplus-project add_dependencies

The sdbusplus-project CMake target no longer exists. sdbusplus is
provided via the recipe sysroot and linked via target_link_libraries,
so the explicit add_dependencies is unnecessary.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [OE-specific]
---
 CMakeLists.txt | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
index 2226050..1234567 100644
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -44,7 +44,6 @@ set (SENSOR_LINK_LIBS -lsystemd stdc++fs sdbusplus)
 
 set (GXPTEMPSENSOR_SRC_FILES src/GxpTempSensor.cpp src/Utils.cpp src/Thresholds.cpp)
 add_executable (gxptempsensor ${GXPTEMPSENSOR_SRC_FILES})
-add_dependencies (gxptempsensor sdbusplus-project)
 target_link_libraries (gxptempsensor ${SENSOR_LINK_LIBS})
 install (TARGETS gxptempsensor RUNTIME DESTINATION bin)
 
